  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3114_2",
    "text": "Nowadays, most middle school students have pocket money every month, and we did a survey in Class 1, Grade 9.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08740120874012088,
      0.12181069958847737,
      0.9093444909344491,
      0.15868312757201647
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3114",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3114_3",
    "text": "As the result shows, amongthe thirty students takingpart in the survey, ost ofthem often buy snacks; about a half spend their pocket money on books, and a few save sore ofit.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08740120874012088,
      0.16263374485596707,
      0.9102742910274291,
      0.19950617283950617
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3114",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3114_4",
    "text": "However, things on me are quitc different. I usully spend most of the money buying good and educational books whichI think make me more knowledgeable. Only a small part is spent on snacks as most of the snacks are in fact unhealthy for us. And I save the rest against a rainy day.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08647140864714087,
      0.20279835390946502,
      0.9093444909344491,
      0.2620576131687243
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3114",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3114_5",
    "text": "It is true that we have more and more pocket money now. Whether we can make good use of it really counts, becausc it ispartly influencing the way we are growing up.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08647140864714087,
      0.2653497942386831,
      0.907484890748489,
      0.3035390946502058
    ],
